<h3>GET : Use following url to get collection of mentioned xero element.</h3>
<hr />
    1.) Get All Accounts: GET http://localhost:61795/api/XeroApi/GetAccounts <br />
    2.) Get All Contacts: GET http://localhost:61795/api/XeroApi/GetContacts <br />
    3.) Get All Invoices: GET http://localhost:61795/api/XeroApi/GetInvoices <br />
    4.) Get All PurchaseOrders: GET http://localhost:61795/api/XeroApi/GetPurchaseOrders <br />

<h3>POST : Use below url to create following xero element</h3>
<hr />

1.) Create Account: POST http://localhost:61795/api/XeroApi/CreateAccount
    Example of creating a account record with minimum element
    
    {
    "Name": "Test Account" ,
    "Type" : "BANK" ,
    "BankAccountNumber" : "121-121-1234567"
    }
2.) Create Contact: POST http://localhost:61795/api/XeroApi/CreateContact
    Example of creating a contact record with minimum element
   
    {
    "Name": "24 locks",
    "FirstName": "Ben",
    "LastName": "Bowden",
    "EmailAddress": "test@example.com"
    }
3.) Create Invoice: POST http://localhost:61795/api/XeroApi/CreateInvoice
    Example of creating a Invoice record
    {
    "Contact": {
            "ContactID": "55024bff-4363-490a-99c3-9d8ea273e9e9"
        },
    "Type":"DRAFT",
    "LineItems": [
            {
                "Description":"Test Invoice",
                "UnitAmount":"25.65",
                "Quantity": "1"         
            }
           ]  
      }      
